 |
 | All Hell Has Broken Loose!!! The Haunted is a fast paced third person
 | action horror game that focuses on delivering an intense multiplayer
 | experience. Your goal is to liberate cursed places and survive the
 | assault from the minions of Hell. The game features several multiplayer
 | modes such as co-op survival, demons vs. humans and demonizer.   
 |
